OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a mostly dry day
OL,6,Fwith patchy cloud allowing plenty of
OL,7,Fbright and sunny spells. The odd
OL,8,Fshower possible in the west in the
OL,9,Fmorning. Winds will be light and
OL,10,Ffeeling a little cooler than in recent
OL,11,Fdays.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA dry evening with clear
OL,14,Fspells becoming more prolonged as
OL,15,Fcloud clears. Remaining dry overnight
OL,16,Fwith mostly clear skies, leading to a
OL,17,Fcold night with a widespread frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
