OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAfter a cold start for many
OL,6,Fit will be a dry day with long spells
OL,7,Fof sunshine. Turning cloudier in the
OL,8,Fevening with some rain.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,11,Fwith outbreaks of rain through Sunday
OL,12,Fand Monday with winds strengthening,
OL,13,Fbut still some good dry and bright or
OL,14,Fsunny spells. A mostly dry day Tuesday
OL,15,Fwith sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
